		<a name="top" id="top"></a>
		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Boston Molasses Disaster</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:322px;"><a href="/wiki/File:BostonMolassesDisaster.jpg" class="image" title="Aftermath of the disaster"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/70/BostonMolassesDisaster.jpg/320px-BostonMolassesDisaster.jpg" width="320" height="254" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:BostonMolassesDisaster.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
Aftermath of the disaster</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>The <b>Boston Molasses Disaster</b>, also known as the <b>Great Molasses Flood</b> and the <b>Great Boston Molasses Tragedy</b>, occurred on January 15, 1919, in the <a href="/wiki/North_End,_Boston" title="North End, Boston">North End</a> neighborhood of <a href="/wiki/Boston,_Massachusetts" title="Boston, Massachusetts" class="mw-redirect">Boston</a>, <a href="/wiki/Massachusetts" title="Massachusetts">Massachusetts</a> in the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a>. A large <a href="/wiki/Molasses" title="Molasses">molasses</a> tank burst, and a wave of molasses rushed through the streets at an estimated 35&#160;mph (56&#160;km/h), killing 21 and injuring 150. The event has entered local folklore, and residents claim that on hot summer days, the area still smells of molasses.<sup id="cite_ref-Smithsonian_0-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Smithsonian-0" title=""><span>[</span>1<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
